A.   
B.   INCLUDE 
C.   include 
D.   INCLUDE 
E.   include
答案：B
備註：在部署過濾器時，可以指定該過濾器要處理哪些請求類型，在web.xml中是利用標籤來設定，有以下五種類型

REQUEST(客戶端請求)(預設值)
FORWARD(透過RequestDispatcher.forward()過來的請求)
INCLUDE(透過RequestDispatcher.include()過來的請求)
ERROR(容器處理例外轉交過來的請求)
ASYNC(Servlet 3.0新增，非同步處理的請求)

使用Annotation時則可如下設定
@WebFilter(
    filterName = "myFilter",
    urlPattern = {"/myFilter"},
    dispatcherTypes = {
            DispatcherType.REQUEST,
            DispatcherType.FORWARD,
            DispatcherType.INCLUDE,
            DispatcherType.ERROR,
            DispatcherType.ASYNC,
    }
)

